agenda.

16:59.585 --> 17:00.553 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

17:00.586 --> 17:01.621 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
PAUL RYAN: Yes, you see the
smile?

17:01.654 --> 17:02.622 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I just -- I love the issue of
tax reform.

17:02.655 --> 17:04.156 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
