17:04.190 --> 17:05.858 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
So, we think it's a
once-in-a-generation
opportunity.

17:05.892 --> 17:08.995 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, here we are,
however many
years that is later, 31 years.

17:09.028 --> 17:10.429 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

17:10.463 --> 17:12.365 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
PAUL RYAN: Yes, I got my
driver's license
the last year we did tax reform.

17:12.398 --> 17:16.836 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Will the
individual and the
corporate tax cuts that you're
interested

17:16.869 --> 17:20.006 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
in the House passing be
permanent?

17:20.039 --> 17:25.044 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
