17:25.077 --> 17:26.045 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

17:26.078 --> 17:27.246 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
PAUL RYAN: Yes and yes.

17:27.280 --> 17:29.115 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Well, to be revenue-neutral,
they will require
offsets.

17:29.148 --> 17:33.486 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
