current Affordable

19:39.445 --> 19:40.479 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Care Act stand?

19:40.513 --> 19:42.281 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

19:42.314 --> 19:46.485 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL RYAN: Yes, so the reason
