health care, which we are
convinced will give

20:16.248 --> 20:18.651 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
us a better system at the end of
the day.

20:18.684 --> 20:22.655 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Remember the promises of
Obamacare, lower
prices, more choices.

20:22.688 --> 20:24.557 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Those things didn't happen.

20:24.590 --> 20:29.228 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We believe we can make good on
those kind
of promises, which is improve
access to affordable

20:29.261 --> 20:30.596 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
