20:37.903 --> 20:40.039 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And that's exactly what we ran
on in 2016.

20:40.072 --> 20:41.607 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Including
preexisting conditions
