health insurance?

21:06.699 --> 21:08.501 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That's a goal we absolutely
share.

21:08.534 --> 21:13.405 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we think there is a better
way of achieving
that goal than Obamacare, which
just so you

