21:28.154 --> 21:28.988 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
PAUL RYAN: Massive price
increases, massive
deductible increases.

21:29.021 --> 21:30.823 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The law is collapsing while we
speak.

21:30.856 --> 21:34.293 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: You have talked
