21:41.333 --> 21:42.268 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That's something we would have
to develop.

21:42.301 --> 21:44.103 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We have asked our Transportation
Committees.

21:44.136 --> 21:49.341 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
