36:03.762 --> 36:06.331 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MELINDA WELSH, Cancer Sufferer:
My name is
Melinda Welsh.

36:06.364 --> 36:11.536 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I'm a writer, and was editor of
The Sacramento
News and Review for around 25
years.

36:11.569 --> 36:18.977 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And when I was diagnosed with
cancer, it just
came naturally, I guess, to
write about it.

36:19.010 --> 36:20.612 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It was shocking to hear.

36:20.645 --> 36:21.913 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
I felt stunned.

36:21.946 --> 36:24.082 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It is squamous cell carcinoma.

36:24.115 --> 36:30.055 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And after we learned that the
cancer had metastasized,
we went to see some specialists.

36:30.088 --> 36:35.193 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I asked each of them how much
time I had left,
and that's when they told me,
you know, six

36:35.226 --> 36:38.730 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to nine months, months to a
year, a year-ish.

36:38.763 --> 36:45.437 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You know, I started writing
again, and I felt
I had something to say that
might mean something

36:45.470 --> 36:50.275 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to other people because of the
lessons I was
learning facing death.

36:50.308 --> 36:56.481 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
"The enormity of the news didn't
sink in fully,
not at first, even after my
doctor uttered

36:56.514 --> 37:00.051 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the words, 'I'm sorry, we did
find cancer.'

37:00.085 --> 37:07.025 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I have turned my attention to
the question,
how do I best spend the time
that I have left?

37:07.058 --> 37:11.930 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
My answer is writing, family and
friends,
the pleasures of small things.

37:11.963 --> 37:15.767 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I was told, don't skip dessert,
