37:15.800 --> 37:20.105 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have taken to getting up a
few early mornings
a week and driving out to see
the sunrise

37:20.138 --> 37:22.974 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
over the flatlands of our mostly
rural county."

37:23.007 --> 37:24.309 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I can't believe this.

37:24.342 --> 37:26.611 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It is going to be a great day.

37:26.644 --> 37:32.784 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
"I will take solace in the idea
that, once
gone, I may come to occupy a
small space in

37:32.817 --> 37:38.756 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the hearts of the people who
loved me most,
