is limited,
life is miraculous, and we are
beautiful."

37:46.498 --> 37:47.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I always loved my life.

37:47.999 --> 37:53.438 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I felt very lucky, my meeting up
with Dave,
my love of my life, best friend.

37:53.471 --> 38:02.747 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
