me want my
life, but more so.

38:02.780 --> 38:05.750 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
After that first piece was
published, we had
a breakthrough.

38:05.783 --> 38:08.953 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I started immunotherapy.

38:08.987 --> 38:15.426 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And Dr. Algazi, who is our -- my
oncologist,
surprises us by showing up in
the infusion

38:15.460 --> 38:16.427 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
room.

38:16.461 --> 38:18.997 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
