giving me a year to live, it was
time to write

39:15.920 --> 39:17.689 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
part two.

39:17.722 --> 39:21.526 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
"In the weeks that followed my
public coming
out about the grim news, a
benevolent tidal

39:21.559 --> 39:26.764 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
