changing the world, or at least
there while

40:33.798 --> 40:36.267 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the world is changing, and
you're able to
really help.

40:36.301 --> 40:40.772 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MELINDA WELSH: Unfortunately,
many people
have cancers that there's no
immunotherapy

40:40.805 --> 40:44.342 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
