happen for certain,
but there's this enormous
potential.

41:14.405 --> 41:16.307 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MELINDA WELSH: We don't want to
hope for too
much.

41:16.341 --> 41:21.412 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We don't want to go into denial
that I have
got this deadly disease that's
trying to kill

41:21.446 --> 41:22.413 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
me.

41:22.447 --> 41:23.681 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
I do.

41:23.715 --> 41:26.284 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
